That's what you said.

10:13.696 --> 10:15.282
No, I meant that...

10:15.323 --> 10:18.243
Lois, please, l-let's...

10:15.323 --> 10:18.243
let's not have this veer off

10:18.285 --> 10:21.329
into us somehow

10:18.285 --> 10:21.329
not having sex tonight.

10:21.371 --> 10:23.664
Oh, God!

10:23.706 --> 10:26.501
Why do they do

10:23.706 --> 10:26.501
