It seems like

10:31.714 --> 10:33.674
the only logical conclusion.

10:33.716 --> 10:35.843
When they're grown and they

10:33.716 --> 10:35.843
have families of their own,

10:35.885 --> 10:37.720
we don't have to let

10:35.885 --> 10:37.720
them visit, do we?

10:37.762 --> 10:39.598
Absolutely not, sweetie.

10:39.639 --> 10:41.558
It's just going to be

10:39.639 --> 10:41.558
you and me,

10:41.600 --> 10:42.683
old and shriveled,

10:42.725 --> 10:45.770
alone in a big, empty house,

10:45.812 --> 10:50.358
the only sound the gentle

10:45.812 --> 10:50.358
sucking of the respirator.

10:50.400 --> 10:52.693
And all our money

10:50.400 --> 10:52.693
will be sitting in a bank

10:52.735 --> 10:54.529
helping no one.

