You guys seen Sara?

11:00.743 --> 11:01.702
No.

11:01.744 --> 11:02.703
That's weird.

11:02.745 --> 11:03.913
She's two minutes late.

11:03.955 --> 11:05.499
Were you supposed

11:03.955 --> 11:05.499
to meet her here?

11:05.540 --> 11:07.292
Well, no, not exactly.

11:07.334 --> 11:08.709
But it was implied.

11:08.751 --> 11:10.587
Implied?

11:10.629 --> 11:11.879
It's our thing.

11:10.629 --> 11:11.879
It's what we do.

11:11.921 --> 11:13.714
We meet at the water

11:11.921 --> 11:13.714
fountain at 8:00.

11:13.756 --> 11:14.715
We're always

11:13.756 --> 11:14.715
within 30 seconds

11:14.757 --> 11:16.134
of each other

11:14.757 --> 11:16.134
in the lunch line,

11:16.176 --> 11:17.594
and when I get home every night,

11:17.636 --> 11:19.179
I wait four minutes

11:17.636 --> 11:19.179
before I call her.

11:19.220 --> 11:20.555
That's how it's always been.

11:20.597 --> 11:21.722
That's our thing.

11:21.764 --> 11:23.433
Wow.

11:23.475 --> 11:25.810
I didn't know having

11:23.475 --> 11:25.810
