11:25.852 --> 11:26.894
It's not creepy!

11:26.936 --> 11:28.104
This is totally normal.

11:28.146 --> 11:29.105
This is dating.

11:29.147 --> 11:30.649
You spend time

11:29.147 --> 11:30.649
with each other,

11:30.689 --> 11:32.233
get to know

11:30.689 --> 11:32.233
each other's habits.

11:32.275 --> 11:34.194
When you're in a relationship,

11:32.275 --> 11:34.194
you'll understand.

11:34.235 --> 11:36.154
But until then, back off.

11:36.196 --> 11:39.782
I'll just hang out

11:36.196 --> 11:39.782
