11:51.419 --> 11:52.837
and making balloon animals.

11:52.879 --> 11:54.381
Does he do trick-shooting?

11:54.422 --> 11:55.756
Well, if he doesn't,

11:55.798 --> 11:57.050
I'm sure we can find

11:55.798 --> 11:57.050
someone who does.

11:57.091 --> 11:59.969
I bet Ronnie'd like

11:57.091 --> 11:59.969
a moonbounce, too.

12:07.060 --> 12:10.146
This relationship is finally

12:07.060 --> 12:10.146
starting to make sense.

