12:19.113 --> 12:20.948
But now it just feels so right.

12:20.990 --> 12:23.076
Wait. What are you doing?

12:20.990 --> 12:23.076
Where are you going?

12:23.117 --> 12:24.785
Home.

12:24.827 --> 12:26.787
We've been kissing

12:24.827 --> 12:26.787
for two hours.

12:26.829 --> 12:27.997
My face is sore.

12:28.039 --> 12:29.374
Yeah, she's right.

12:29.416 --> 12:30.875
We can't make out all day.

12:30.917 --> 12:32.793
We've both got our own things

12:30.917 --> 12:32.793
to do.

12:32.835 --> 12:35.088
She's so smart when it comes

12:32.835 --> 12:35.088
to these things.

12:35.129 --> 12:36.881
If you're seeing someone else,

12:35.129 --> 12:36.881
