12:36.923 --> 12:38.799
What?!

12:38.841 --> 12:40.260
I'm sorry.

12:40.301 --> 12:42.220
I don't know where

12:40.301 --> 12:42.220
that came from.

12:42.262 --> 12:44.805
Look, I got to go home.

12:44.847 --> 12:46.765
I'll call you tonight.

12:50.019 --> 12:51.896
That was pathetic.

12:51.938 --> 12:53.814
You were watching us?!

12:53.856 --> 12:55.400
Believe me,

12:53.856 --> 12:55.400
it's the last time.

12:55.442 --> 12:57.110
You know, just because

12:55.442 --> 12:57.110
you have a girl

12:57.151 --> 12:58.986
doesn't mean

12:57.151 --> 12:58.986
