12:59.028 --> 13:01.615
I don't know what's wrong

12:59.028 --> 13:01.615
with her.

13:01.656 --> 13:02.823
She's driving me crazy.

13:02.865 --> 13:05.285
I freak out, like,

13:02.865 --> 13:05.285
20 times a day.

13:05.326 --> 13:07.621
Dude, you think

13:05.326 --> 13:07.621
