13:07.662 --> 13:10.081
You just got to calm down,

13:07.662 --> 13:10.081
turn off your brain.

13:10.123 --> 13:11.249
It's not that easy.

13:11.291 --> 13:13.251
Sure, it is.

13:11.291 --> 13:13.251
I do it all the time.

13:13.293 --> 13:14.628
Watch.

13:14.669 --> 13:16.504
You can't just

13:14.669 --> 13:16.504
turn off your...

13:16.546 --> 13:18.548
Reese?

13:18.590 --> 13:19.840
Reese?

13:19.882 --> 13:21.760
Whoa...

13:21.800 --> 13:23.344
How long was I out?

13:23.386 --> 13:26.681
BROCK:

13:23.386 --> 13:26.681
And as I pulled her

13:23.386 --> 13:26.681
from the wreckage,

13:26.723 --> 13:30.727
she was so disfigured

13:30.769 --> 13:34.897
that I didn't even know

13:30.769 --> 13:34.897
it was my own sister!

13:34.939 --> 13:37.066
VANESSA:

13:34.939 --> 13:37.066
Don't worry.

13:37.108 --> 13:38.652
Dimitri is the finest

13:38.693 --> 13:40.153
reconstructive surgeon

13:38.693 --> 13:40.153
in the state.

13:40.194 --> 13:42.697
Who's Dimitri?

13:42.739 --> 13:44.741
The head of

13:42.739 --> 13:44.741
Municipal Hospital.

13:44.783 --> 13:46.867
He and Vanessa had an affair

13:44.783 --> 13:46.867
last year, then he...

13:46.909 --> 13:48.911
Shut up in there!

13:51.164 --> 13:53.583
Oh, man, who's got their

13:51.164 --> 13:53.583
assignment on Cambodia?

13:53.625 --> 13:54.875
I need to borrow it.

13:54.917 --> 13:57.878
Where were you... last night?

13:57.920 --> 13:58.879
What?

13:58.921 --> 14:01.508
The  Space 1999  marathon

14:01.549 --> 14:02.883
