14:02.925 --> 14:06.471
I made you a tunic.

14:02.925 --> 14:06.471
And a hologram badge.

14:06.513 --> 14:07.972
Dabney, I...

14:06.513 --> 14:07.972
Forget it!

14:08.014 --> 14:10.684
I gave it to my

14:08.014 --> 14:10.684
mom's boyfriend.

14:10.725 --> 14:12.143
Thanks for nothing.

14:12.185 --> 14:14.187
Guys, look, I'm sorry.

14:14.228 --> 14:15.896
I've just been...

14:15.938 --> 14:18.692
Sara and I were on the phone...

14:18.733 --> 14:21.110
Never mind, I'm just sorry.

14:22.945 --> 14:25.990
I promise

14:22.945 --> 14:25.990
this won't happen again.

14:26.032 --> 14:28.368
I think I turned a corner

14:26.032 --> 14:28.368
on this thing.

14:28.409 --> 14:31.746
Sara and I were talking,

14:28.409 --> 14:31.746
and, uh, it just came to me.

14:32.955 --> 14:36.083
I think we worked things out.

14:36.125 --> 14:38.127
Can you guys excuse me for

14:36.125 --> 14:38.127
a second? I'll be right back.

14:40.797 --> 14:43.842
He does seem... sorry.

14:43.883 --> 14:46.010
I say we cancel our

14:43.883 --> 14:46.010
vote of censure.

14:46.052 --> 14:47.928
I second that.

14:47.970 --> 14:51.974
After all, he was there for us

14:47.970 --> 14:51.974
after the Arboretum burnt down.

14:52.016 --> 14:54.394
And how can you

14:52.016 --> 14:54.394
look in those eyes

14:54.435 --> 14:56.730
and say no to

14:54.435 --> 14:56.730
anything he asks?

14:56.771 --> 14:58.356
(both sigh)

14:58.398 --> 15:01.901
I think... he's learned...

14:58.398 --> 15:01.901
his lesson.

15:08.991 --> 15:12.453
Okay, only two

15:08.991 --> 15:12.453
invitations left.

15:12.495 --> 15:13.954
Ronnie's going to

15:12.495 --> 15:13.954
have a moonbounce

15:13.996 --> 15:15.248
and a make-your-own-sundae cart.

15:15.289 --> 15:16.332
I'll go.

15:16.374 --> 15:17.751
Maybe you will.

15:17.792 --> 15:19.586
What kind of present

15:17.792 --> 15:19.586
