15:19.627 --> 15:20.587
Skateboard.

15:20.628 --> 15:22.213
Excellent choice.

15:22.255 --> 15:24.965
Ronnie already has

15:22.255 --> 15:24.965
a brand-new skateboard.

15:25.007 --> 15:27.886
Why don't you let me

15:25.007 --> 15:27.886
worry about Ronnie?

15:29.303 --> 15:32.265
Sit.

15:32.306 --> 15:33.683
Look at yourself.

15:33.725 --> 15:35.393
They put you on probation.

15:35.435 --> 15:36.770
Probation!

15:36.811 --> 15:38.271
If you do just

15:38.312 --> 15:39.856
one more thing wrong,

15:39.898 --> 15:41.441
they're going to kick

15:39.898 --> 15:41.441
you out of school!

15:41.482 --> 15:43.359
Do you have any idea

15:41.482 --> 15:43.359
how serious this is?

15:43.401 --> 15:45.152
Is this who you

15:43.401 --> 15:45.152
want to be?

15:45.194 --> 15:46.987
You want to be some

15:45.194 --> 15:46.987
little lapdog

15:47.029 --> 15:48.907
who ruins his life

15:47.029 --> 15:48.907
for some girl?

15:48.948 --> 15:50.241
For God's sake, Malcolm,

15:50.283 --> 15:52.410
you beat up a foreign

15:50.283 --> 15:52.410
exchange student!

15:52.452 --> 15:53.994
Poor little Zadoc

15:54.036 --> 15:56.205
left his country to get away

15:54.036 --> 15:56.205
from this kind of abuse!

15:57.123 --> 15:58.875
Are you even

15:57.123 --> 15:58.875
listening to me?

15:58.917 --> 16:00.293
Yes, I'm listening!

16:00.334 --> 16:02.796
But you know what, Mom?

16:00.334 --> 16:02.796
I've got bigger problems!

16:02.837 --> 16:04.004
You may not have noticed,

16:04.046 --> 16:06.048
but I've been screwing up

16:04.046 --> 16:06.048
a lot lately.

16:06.090 --> 16:07.842
All because

16:06.090 --> 16:07.842
of some stupid girl.

16:07.884 --> 16:09.218
I'm on probation!

16:09.260 --> 16:11.596
I beat up a kid

16:09.260 --> 16:11.596
who doesn't even speak English!

16:11.638 --> 16:13.264
I am going through

16:11.638 --> 16:13.264
a lot right now,

16:13.306 --> 16:15.349
and you don't even care!

16:17.560 --> 16:19.103
VANESSA:

16:17.560 --> 16:19.103
We can still

16:19.145 --> 16:20.730
pull this off.

16:20.772 --> 16:22.482
You'll never pass the

16:20.772 --> 16:22.482
DNA test, Vanessa.

16:22.523 --> 16:24.943
And even your lies aren't

16:22.523 --> 16:24.943
going to be enough this time.

16:24.984 --> 16:28.947
But, Brock, if you didn't buy

16:24.984 --> 16:28.947
the mining rights, then who did?

16:28.988 --> 16:31.031
BROCK:

16:28.988 --> 16:31.031
Don't either of you two

16:28.988 --> 16:31.031
see what's going on?

16:31.073 --> 16:32.617
The person who bought

16:31.073 --> 16:32.617
the mining rights

16:32.659 --> 16:34.034
is the same person

16:34.076 --> 16:35.912
who stole Mrs. Bronson's

16:34.076 --> 16:35.912
diamond brooch.

16:35.954 --> 16:37.413
And the person

16:35.954 --> 16:37.413
who ran Nathaniel's car

16:37.455 --> 16:38.748
off the road that night.

16:38.790 --> 16:40.040
That person's name is...

16:40.082 --> 16:41.501
Okay, you're free to go.

16:41.542 --> 16:43.127
Shh!

16:41.542 --> 16:43.127
Come on, move it!

16:43.169 --> 16:45.296
What? No, no, no!

16:43.169 --> 16:45.296
You can't do this to me.

16:45.338 --> 16:46.714
Just give me five

16:45.338 --> 16:46.714
more minutes!

16:46.756 --> 16:47.674
Let's go.

16:47.715 --> 16:49.049
Wait! No! hang on!

16:49.091 --> 16:50.217
Wait, it was the mayor, right?

16:50.259 --> 16:51.636
No, the Widow Farthington!

16:51.678 --> 16:53.053
And what about

16:51.678 --> 16:53.053
