16:53.095 --> 16:54.054
Oh, no, no, no!

16:54.096 --> 16:55.055
His amnesiac brother!

16:55.097 --> 16:56.056
(shrieks)

16:56.098 --> 16:57.266
(door slamming)

16:57.308 --> 16:59.143
(bell ringing)

16:59.185 --> 17:01.061
I didn't understand one word

17:01.103 --> 17:02.730
that was said

17:01.103 --> 17:02.730
in the last six hours.

17:02.772 --> 17:04.064
I'm exhausted.

17:04.106 --> 17:06.359
I couldn't sleep all night.

17:06.400 --> 17:09.320
But I finally figured out

17:06.400 --> 17:09.320
what I got to do.

17:09.362 --> 17:10.697
Sara, wait up!

17:12.907 --> 17:15.075
Look, I've done a lot

17:12.907 --> 17:15.075
of thinking,

17:15.117 --> 17:17.077
and we need to talk.

17:17.119 --> 17:18.746
Sara, this just isn't working.

17:18.788 --> 17:20.164
Since I've known you,

17:20.206 --> 17:22.333
I've been nothing

17:20.206 --> 17:22.333
but obsessive and neurotic

17:22.375 --> 17:25.503
and a totally jealous creep

17:22.375 --> 17:25.503
who's way too clingy.

17:25.545 --> 17:27.087
I don't like

17:25.545 --> 17:27.087
what this relationship

17:27.129 --> 17:29.089
has turned me into, so...

17:29.131 --> 17:30.090
I got you this pager.

17:30.132 --> 17:31.885
What?

17:30.132 --> 17:31.885
It's perfect.

17:31.926 --> 17:33.970
See, now we'll know exactly

17:31.926 --> 17:33.970
where the other one is

17:34.012 --> 17:36.096
every second of the day.

17:34.012 --> 17:36.096
No more worry, no more doubt.

17:36.138 --> 17:37.932
We'll finally be able

17:36.138 --> 17:37.932
to trust each other.

17:37.974 --> 17:39.099
It's perfect.

17:39.141 --> 17:41.060
We have to

17:39.141 --> 17:41.060
break up, Malcolm.

17:42.770 --> 17:44.731
I don't think you heard me.

17:44.772 --> 17:47.274
In fact, I'm proposing

17:44.772 --> 17:47.274
the exact opposite of that.

17:47.316 --> 17:49.151
That's what the pager's for.

17:49.193 --> 17:51.153
I'm sorry.

17:51.195 --> 17:54.323
Good-bye.

17:56.158 --> 17:57.159
No.

17:57.201 --> 17:59.704
No! No!

17:59.746 --> 18:01.706
Sara!

18:01.748 --> 18:03.416
(echoing)

18:03.457 --> 18:05.209
You can't break up with me!

18:05.251 --> 18:08.170
Because I am filled with nothing

18:05.251 --> 18:08.170
but love and good feelings

18:08.212 --> 18:10.924
and no anger and no jealousy.

18:10.965 --> 18:13.133
And none of those bad things

18:10.965 --> 18:13.133
that will lead to you

18:13.175 --> 18:14.510
not wanting to

18:13.175 --> 18:14.510
be with me!

18:14.552 --> 18:15.636
Okay, fine!

18:15.678 --> 18:17.221
Get out of here!

18:17.263 --> 18:18.723
I don't need you anyway!

18:18.765 --> 18:19.724
I hate your guts!

18:19.766 --> 18:20.808
I never needed you!

18:20.850 --> 18:23.185
No, no, no, no.

18:23.227 --> 18:24.729
I love you!

18:24.771 --> 18:26.146
I always have!

18:26.188 --> 18:27.815
I always will!

18:27.857 --> 18:30.526
We were meant to be together!

18:30.568 --> 18:33.362
I gave you my soul, Sara!

18:33.404 --> 18:34.864
I gave it to you!

18:34.906 --> 18:36.156
My soul!

18:36.198 --> 18:38.034
My soul...

18:38.868 --> 18:41.996
Sara!

18:50.630 --> 18:52.172
♪ Yippie ki-yay ♪

18:52.214 --> 18:54.634
♪ Just rolled off his tongue ♪

18:54.675 --> 18:56.176
♪ That's how the West

18:54.675 --> 18:56.176
