18:56.218 --> 18:57.887
MRS. DeMARCO:

18:56.218 --> 18:57.887
Here you go, sweetheart.

18:57.929 --> 19:00.180
You know, I always thought

18:57.929 --> 19:00.180
you hated cookie dough.

19:00.222 --> 19:01.808
So, are you having a good time?

19:01.849 --> 19:03.183
Yeah, Mom.

19:03.225 --> 19:04.184
Thanks.

19:04.226 --> 19:06.186
Well, you really

19:04.226 --> 19:06.186
should thank Dewey, too.

19:06.228 --> 19:08.856
He was a big help

19:06.228 --> 19:08.856
