(laughing):

19:10.149 --> 19:12.192
I got you!

19:12.234 --> 19:13.861
You're dead!

19:15.237 --> 19:16.990
You ruined my birthday!

19:17.031 --> 19:18.491
I hate you!

19:18.532 --> 19:22.161
I've had two sundaes

19:18.532 --> 19:22.161
