19:23.245 --> 19:25.581
Malcolm, let go.

19:25.623 --> 19:27.500
Come on, come on.

19:27.541 --> 19:30.377
I can't feel my fingers.

19:30.419 --> 19:32.212
Hey, I'll go get us

19:30.419 --> 19:32.212
some more punch.

19:32.254 --> 19:33.422
How does that

19:32.254 --> 19:33.422
sound, huh?

19:36.843 --> 19:39.219
You know, son, this is

19:36.843 --> 19:39.219
all part of growing up.

19:39.261 --> 19:41.681
You're just going to

19:39.261 --> 19:41.681
have to get used to it.

19:47.561 --> 19:50.314
No, I don't.

19:50.356 --> 19:52.692
